items ({({"plains","The plains consists of a series of gently rolling hills which stretches off as far as the eye can see. They are all barren and bare being covered in dead or dieing grass only","hills","These hills make up the plains area. They are covered in dead grass","grass","Dead grass which crunches as you walk on it","sky","The sky is a dark and angry grey colour presaging the coming of heavy rains",}),({"plains","Barren and sterile hills","rock wall","A sheer black rock wall which almost appears to have been polished it is so smooth. There are no hand or footholds in it and it is smooth and cool to the touch.","wall","A sheer black rock wall which almost appears to have been polished it is so smooth. There are no hand or footholds in it and it is smooth and cool to the touch.","rock","A queer sort of rock which glistens wetly. It is smooth and cool to the touch. You wonder how it was shaped and what made it so smooth.","clouds","Dark and heavy clouds which definately carry more than a promise of drenching rains","portal","A strange doorway covered in a translucent shield which appears to fade in and out of your vision","shield","As you examine the shield you accidently touch it and discover it is rock hard. You cannmot penetrate it try as hard as you can","ground","Dry and dusty the ground consists of a loose soil which you estimate would easily be blown away in the first heavy winds.",}),({"flat area","This is the plains","hills","In the distance to the south can be seen the hills from which you have just come. They are brown and dead looking.","clouds","The clouds here are thick and dark","creek","A small shallow creek. You are unable to locate the point at which it starts or to find the point at which it ends","house","A small house. It is roughly built out of whole logs fitted togethor. The roof is covered in wooden shingles which are darkened with age and covered in areas with moss and lichens. There is an open door in fron of you.",}),0,0,({"cavern",